Troubleshooting Tips
Services won't start:

Check Docker logs: docker-compose logs -f
Verify port availability: netstat -tulpn | grep -E '9000|9001|9200'
Ensure sufficient memory: free -h
Authentication failures:

Verify token files exist in /tmp
Check token format (should include "Bearer" prefix)
Re-run initialization scripts
API requests fail:

Confirm services are running: docker ps
Test connectivity: curl http://localhost:9000/api/status
Check firewall rules: sudo ufw status
